  carbohydrates: 32 g
  sugar: 24 g
  protein: 26 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 1400 mg
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pork-egg-roll-in-a-bowl-627a6f1a72bc7cf6dd023d54
